Text: "Feeling free.\nNo expectations, no plans, no chains.\nJust Wandering around\
  \ feeling everything, colors, people, alleys. Feeling history/writing history.\n\
  \nThe wind is in favor.\n\n It is so easy when i stop caring,maybe that is the lesson."
